title: Problems?
body:
Me and my friend having abit of problems with the game and starting the match.
When i start the game it might crash or get stuck or not accept or just show us that we didnt pick or something in the odd.
can someone tell me whats going on ?..

replies.body: It looks like you're on the EUNE server which has been having a few problems I'm noticing today. The [**status page**](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune) shows that ranked is still disabled, and we do still have some people looking into what's going on.
